AngToForward (script event)
===========================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game\_class) type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Returns a forward vector for the given Euler angles.

Usage
-----

*vector* angToForward( *vector* **angles** )

Parameters
----------

-   [angles] - A vector that's indivudual components correspond with heading, pitch, and bank angles.

